title: Dog Bandanas 2 Pack, Triangle Pet Scarf, Sheer Chiffon Fabric, Bandana for Small Medium Large Dogs and Cats, Check Plaid Vintage Art Purple Blue

Matching Dog and Owner Outfits: Set of 2 pack. Whether traveling, taking photos, daily walking or at home, it’s full of love when you and your pets are wearing the bandanas with the same pattern.
Special Gift: Ideal holiday season gifts for dog owners on Christmas party, Thanksgiving day, Birthday party, Mother's Day, Father's Day, Valentine's Day.

Exclusive Customization: We provide personalized customization service, we can print your favorite pattern or text on this bandana, and the pixel of the picture is required to be no less than 2000x2000.
